\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
\fITimeout\fR is invalid.

.RE


.RE

noconnection
.RS 2
The connection to 
\fINode\fR was lost or could not be established. The function may or may not be applied.

.RE

system_limit
.RS 2
The 
\fIerpc\fR operation failed due to some system limit being reached. This typically due to failure to create a process on the remote node \fINode\fR, but can be other things as well.

.RE

timeout
.RS 2
The 
\fIerpc\fR operation timed out. The function may or may not be applied.

.RE

notsup
.RS 2
The remote node 
\fINode\fR does not support this \fIerpc\fR operation.

.RE


.RE


